{"tid":2278350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃子悅: 啱啱去探望鍾翰林 佢精神狀態唔錯 主要睇小說打發時間","createTime":"2020-11-09T05:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T07:31:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8baeecf8d12d4cd6d0091a4595cf61d7ecbcf075","tid":2278350,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"黃子悅 Wong Ji Yuet:<br />\n<br />\n啱啱去咗壁屋懲教所探望鍾翰林<br />\n佢精神狀態唔錯 有講有笑<br />\n頭髮長咗少少 睇黎細個咗<br />\n喺入面無受到唔好嘅對待 <br />\n主要睇下小說黎打發時間<br />\n睇到佢好天真咁笑嘅樣其實好心痛<br />\n但都慶幸佢至少過得還可以<br />\nP.s. 警察今早以「協助疑犯潛逃」的罪名拘捕一名人士，據悉與鍾翰林企圖進入美國領事館一事有關。啱啱都告知左佢此事。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n#黃子悅<br />\n📸IG ｜wongjiyuet153<br />\n🌎Twitter ｜wongjiyuet<br />\n📽Youtube｜黃子悅<br />\n🤳🏻FB ｜黃子悅 Wong Ji Yuet<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wongjiyuet97/posts/195184412046182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwongjiyuet97%2Fposts%2F195184412046182&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=2e61ff01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wongjiyuet97/posts/195184412046182</a>"},{"pid":"b536a51b8265383930d48777c5617055d355bdae","tid":2278350,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f35317fe14c9eeee0d561e606d1d4e800b17e65","tid":2278350,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bcf2921ce021fda5432295ca3988e6f05247af","tid":2278350,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"